OL,3,CDesigner bread bins and video games:
OL,4,CHow did Murrell spend the embezzled
OL,5,Cmoney?
OL,7,FA #1,200 space telescope, a designer
OL,8,Fbread bin costing #60 and two toilet
OL,9,Fseats for nearly #70 are some of the
OL,10,Fitems Peter Murrell bought using money
OL,11,Fhe embezzled from the SNP.
OL,13,FHe also bought three designer manicure
OL,14,Fsets for nearly #294, DVDs of the
OL,15,FDanish political thriller Borgen, a
OL,16,FGrand Theft Auto V video game and a
OL,17,Fdesigner egg poacher set for nearly
OL,18,F#24.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
