OL,3,CDesigner bread bins and video games:
OL,4,CHow did Murrell spend the embezzled
OL,5,Cmoney?
OL,7,FAlso among his purchases were a Jura
OL,8,FGiga 5 Cromo coffee machine for nearly
OL,9,F#3,232 ` and a book of speeches by his
OL,10,Festranged wife, Nicola Sturgeon.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThe 126-page indictment details
OL,18,Fhundreds of things Murrell bought
OL,19,Fusing the embezzled funds.
