OL,3,CDesigner bread bins and video games:
OL,4,CHow did Murrell spend the embezzled
OL,5,Cmoney?
OL,7,FSome of the items purchased with the
OL,8,Fembezzled money include:
OL,10,FThe former chief executive, who is
OL,11,FNicola Sturgeon's estranged husband,
OL,12,Fwas charged with embezzling the funds
OL,13,Ffrom the Scottish National Party
OL,14,Fbetween August 2010 and October 2022.
OL,16,FMurrell, 61, arrived at the High Court
OL,17,Fon Monday wearing a black suit with a
OL,18,Fblack tie and sentencing is due to
OL,19,Ftake place on June 23.
